rows.label: qev014303_MSG0001
rows.name: Ah ha! Aaaah ha ha ha ha ha ha![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0002
rows.name: I fooound yooou![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0003
rows.name:
Ah ha ha! I knew you'd come! I KNEW it!
You had to come and try to kill Alex![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0004
rows.name:
That's how you are. WHAT you are. Humans live to
kill each other. Ah ha ha ha ha! It's too funny![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0005
rows.name: Aw, don't be so stiff. Come on! Let's play![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0006
rows.name:
Oh, Aleeex? I won the bet. May I also keep this alien
as a toy to play with?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0007
rows.name:
Do whatever you like, so long as you stop that
earsplitting laughter.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0008
rows.name: But first, I need your help.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0009
rows.name: Aaaaah ha ha ha! You got it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0010
rows.name:
Once I kill you, who will come to kill Alex next?
Ah ha! Aaah ha ha ha! I can't wait![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0011
rows.name: Aaah ha ha ha! We lost! Ha ha ha! Boooo![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0012
rows.name: *cough* H-hey, look. Blood. Ha ha! Weird![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0013
rows.name: I... Huh? I c-can't stand... Pffffffkheh heh...heh...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0014
rows.name:
Aaaah ha ha ha! Look! My hand! My right hand
is broken! Ha ha ha! Oh, it hurts so much!
IT HURTS! AAAAAH HA HA HA![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0015
rows.name: I didn't anticipate you sniffing us out here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_JNK0010
rows.name: Explain

rows.label: qev014303_SEL0011
rows.name: Tell Alex about the Nopon informant.

rows.label: qev014303_JNK0020
rows.name: Accuse

rows.label: qev014303_SEL0021
rows.name: Claim that Alex brought this upon himself.

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0016
rows.name: Hmph! Filthy animals. Not that it matters now...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0017
rows.name:
I'd planned to cast aside these Ganglion scum when
they ceased to be of use.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0018
rows.name: But you and Eliza have meddled at every turn...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0019
rows.name: Then I am to blame for all this? How amusing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0020
rows.name:
You're a blind follower of that ignorant girl!
A puppetâ€”nothing more![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0021
rows.name:
Just remember that being victorious doesn't mean
that you are right...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0022
rows.name: My back is to the wall, and yet you seem so calm.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0023
rows.name:
Did you never consider I might have allies lying in
ambush, you credulous fool?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0024
rows.name:
Heh... Now that I think about it, I doubt heaven or hell
awaits fabricated beings like us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0025
rows.name: Is this...the end I hoped to meet...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0026
rows.name:
Eliza... Wh-what happened...?
We used to see eye to...eye...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0027
rows.name: Heh... Heh ha ha ha![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0028
rows.name: Do not think this future of yours will come...blood free...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0029
rows.name: Heh heh heh... Ahh ha ha ha ha![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014303_MSG0030
rows.name: Ah ha ha! Hah...hggk...[ST:wait ]
